import React from 'react'
import {Header} from '../components/Header/Header'
import { Slide } from '../components/Slide/Slide'
import { Category } from '../components/Category/Category'
import {Item} from '../components/Product/Item'
import { TopSearchProduct } from '../components/TopSearchProduct/TopSearchProduct'
import { ShopMall } from '../components/ShopMall/ShopMall'
import { Banner } from '../components/Banner/Banner'

export const Home = () => {
  const bannerImages = [
    "https://cf.shopee.vn/file/vn-11134258-7ra0g-m805ryoe5ls2ef",
    "https://cf.shopee.vn/file/vn-50009109-727a24a85a60935da5ccb9008298f681"
  ];
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
    <Slide/>
    <Category/>
    <ShopMall/>
    <TopSearchProduct/>
    <Item/>
    <Banner images={bannerImages}>

    </Banner>
    </>
  )
}
